{"tid":705531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佐迪艾巴被爆不滿迪基亞：廢物！","createTime":"2018-06-17T08:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T09:06:34.000Z","uid":13543,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"843e4d8325ae8f62f58f10fd3c1e16257833de22","tid":705531,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/06/17/1/15b6df4aba8fa22c0987ac66567a653e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F1%2F15b6df4aba8fa22c0987ac66567a653e.jpg&h=4af838f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在葡萄牙與西班牙的比賽中，C.朗拿度超神發揮完成帽子戲法，3-3的結果對於葡萄牙來說非常振奮人心，但對於西班牙來說卻有點難以接受。<br />\n<br />\n　　迪基亞在今場比賽中完全被C.朗拿度擊敗，他先是牛油手失誤，被C.朗拿度遠射破門，最後時刻還被C.朗拿度自由球攻破。葡萄牙一共3腳命中門框的射門，迪基亞一球也沒撲出去。<br />\n<br />\n　　被譽為當今球壇第一門神的他在今場賽後遭受質疑，隊友似乎亦對他有所抱怨。在西班牙Cuatro的轉播鏡頭中，艾巴就對迪基亞的表現十分不滿。<br />\n<br />\n　　畫面顯示，在迪基亞失掉最後那個自由球後，艾巴顯得很無奈，他搖頭攤手，嘴裡還念叨著：「這XX真是廢物。」<br />\n<br />\n　　（路易）"},{"pid":"db11ef17a8ef4127d6712780df42a8052a614367","tid":705531,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:53:58.000Z","msg":"賓度同華迪斯,卡斯守仲好啦"},{"pid":"f6b619197d63ca396f2b8e953ce10c0acb293017","tid":705531,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:57:56.000Z","msg":"這獌狗真是廢物"},{"pid":"0d743d49e715d9a1dedb48d41e9c048163e11e2f","tid":705531,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"一定係拿祖搞事<br />\n早就應該選羅拔圖"},{"pid":"2fb2b1da0391049c0badcc7d62f8ca2dd8368e8f","tid":705531,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"後防勁就顯得龍門廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c20d57d17ba478ff9f7564dcc1274db607f6fd8","tid":705531,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"死仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞內訌"}]}